Someone to provide guidance on planning, scheduling, procurement, and all the execution and tracking related activities involving Data and Artificial intelligence (AI) projects within the organization
Mandatory Skill-set
Degree in Business Computing, Finance, Information Technology, Computer Science, Engineering, Business or Data Science;
