Sound knowledge in financial management to ensure project financials are up to date and correctly captured in a timely manner;
Analytical, articulate and able to communicate comfortably with various stakeholders such as project sponsors, project managers, data scientist, platform leads, business units;
Comfortable with O365 tools, Word, Excel, PowerPoint, SharePoint;
Skilled at problem solving, planning and organizing;
Excellent written, presentation and communication skills.
